Peanut Butter Milkshake

5 min
$4.5
600 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

dairypeanuts

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Dessert

Tags:

dessertbeveragequickeasy

Description

A creamy and indulgent milkshake that satisfies your sweet tooth with the rich flavor of peanut butter.

Ingredients

  • vanilla ice cream: 2 cups
  • milk: 1 cup
  • peanut butter: 3 tablespoons
  • honey (optional): 1 tablespoon
  • whipped cream (for topping): optional
